data.title: The Kyle & Jackie O Show
data.meta_description: Australia's #1 radio show. Kyle & Jackie O are joined every day by the world's biggest stars on KIIS. Get the FULL SHOW on demand daily, plus mini best-bit episodes for your quick fix.
data.text:
Amy Shark joins us on Kyle & Jackie O's Songbook stage to perform a cover of 'Fast Car' along with her newest single 'Gone'. Have a listen to hear her performance + some juicy goss...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

We had Alex join us in the studio for a game of Guess The Fetish! By Q&A and process of elimination, Kyle & Jackie try and figure out what gets this guy going! The result is...gross. Have a listen!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

On today's 'Remember Me' we surprise Jackie with a blast from her past that has held a grudge for over 20 years! She came in live to confront Jackie for 'ruining her life'. Have a listen to how it all unfolded...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

In breaking news straight from The Eras Tour, Taylor Swift has announced her Vienna shows will be cancelled after terrorist attacks have been confirmed. Have a listen for full details...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

A 29 year old brave mother in Ballarat was confronted by an offender who was armed with a shotgun. It didn't stop her from chasing him down though! Have a listen as Ash Trezise gives us a play by play of how it all went down... prepare for some swearing...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

We chat to Colin McLaren who is a former undercover cop... Colin gives us the inside on what it's like, the crazy positions he's been put in and how to identify an undercover cop! Listen for all his crazy stories.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

We surprised Kyle with an old friend he hasn't seen in over 20 years! Have a listen as they go down memory lane all the way back to when Kyle was homeless...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

This confession booth was a tough one. Lara was given the responsibility of taking care of her best friend Holly's dog's ashes. Holly LOVED her dog and was heartbroken when they spread the ashes. But Lara needs to get something off her chest... she dropped the ashes and replaced them with dirt. Have a listen to hear her tell Holly live on air...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

Jackie was shocked to find out something Kyle had kept from her about a conversation he had with her ex-husband. Have a listen to hear the confession...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

Following an O News story about psychopaths in Hollywood, Kyle & Jackie decided to put themselves to the test - are they psychopaths? Are YOU are psychopath? Test yourself!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

Bonnie Blue joins us live in studio to chat about her (sex) work and how she feels sorry for men as they just want to have a buffet of options, even in a relationship. Bonnie explains how to successfully cheat in a relationship and believes it ok. Jackie, not so much. Have a listen as the two go head to head...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
